People who visited neighborhood
libraries, who participated

00:52:08.830 --> 00:52:14.150
in programming were invited
to create posters of their own

00:52:14.150 --> 00:52:17.860
that address social and
political and cultural issues

00:52:17.860 --> 00:52:19.760
that affected them directly.

00:52:19.760 --> 00:52:24.240
And like 50 years before,
they were [inaudible]

00:52:24.240 --> 00:52:25.540
&gt;&gt; Nick Petr: Sorry.

00:52:25.540 --> 00:52:26.840
&gt;&gt; Unidentified Speaker:

00:52:26.840 --> 00:52:29.490
