says something

00:52:29.490 --> 00:52:31.430
about our community today.

00:52:31.430 --> 00:52:35.260
I think it's direct
engagement, it is story sharing,

00:52:35.260 --> 00:52:38.930
it's getting people from
different generations to look

00:52:38.930 --> 00:52:42.080
at a moment in history
with new eyes.

00:52:42.080 --> 00:52:44.140
It gets them to tell
their own stories.

00:52:44.140 --> 00:52:46.250
I think it's an excellent
way for us

00:52:46.250 --> 00:52:49.940
to connect communities
to our collections.

