02:48:48.440 --> 02:48:50.030
Which I think is telling.

02:48:50.030 --> 02:48:51.800
You know that this was
a moment, you know,

02:48:51.800 --> 02:48:54.870
in black power civil rights and
a whole range of things going on

02:48:54.870 --> 02:48:58.610
and that even in a, in a
school, I mean in a city

02:48:58.610 --> 02:49:00.480
