02:51:25.260 --> 02:51:28.410
&gt;&gt; Taquiena Boston:
June 19, 1968.

02:51:28.410 --> 02:51:31.310
Today my sister and
I bought ice cream.

02:51:31.310 --> 02:51:35.310
I didn't go out today, I
