03:09:22.500 --> 03:09:24.680
And in teaching us this
history, the one thing

03:09:24.680 --> 03:09:28.980
that they made sure we
did was that we sang.

03:09:28.980 --> 03:09:31.910
And they were planting
something in us then

03:09:31.910 --> 03:09:34.080
