With the troubles of the world.

03:10:06.620 --> 03:10:09.130
The kids going what?

03:10:09.130 --> 03:10:13.320
Now this, that's
not the good part.

03:10:13.320 --> 03:10:20.130
Then I get to the part, I'm
going home to live with God.

03:10:20.130 --> 03:10:23.190
And they're going, and
that was the expression

03:10:23.190 --> 03:10:25.090
