03:13:09.970 --> 03:13:11.610
What is the nature of goodness,

03:13:11.610 --> 03:13:13.790
if you don't have
a particular faith?

03:13:13.790 --> 03:13:17.140
What is the nature
of our better angels?

03:13:17.140 --> 03:13:21.900
And now let's take this music
and let's weigh them to see,

03:13:21.900 --> 03:13:24.850
how can we pull the
goodness from this music?

03:13:24.850 --> 03:13:27.270
How can we serve humanity?

03:13:27.270 --> 03:13:30.570
How can we lift each
other through this music?

03:13:30.570 --> 03:13:34.660
