quotes from the '68 campaign

03:57:47.320 --> 03:57:48.710
where young people
that are living

03:57:48.710 --> 03:57:51.980
at that Resurrection
City say, you know,

03:57:51.980 --> 03:57:56.420
in my lifetime this environment
is going to be a major issue.

03:57:56.420 --> 03:57:59.260
I mean because people could
see that the degrading of life

03:57:59.260 --> 03:58:02.600
and everything, like
what, you know, how,

03:58:02.600 --> 03:58:03.900
how important that was.

03:58:03.900 --> 03:58:06.920
And so, but then we've
also realized that,

03:58:06.920 --> 03:58:09.990
that what ties those
four evils together,

03:58:09.990 --> 03:58:14.870
what ties systemic racism,
systemic poverty, militarism

03:58:14.870 --> 03:58:16.170
and the war economy

03:58:16.170 --> 03:58:18.990
and ecological devastation
together is a distorted

03:58:18.990 --> 03:58:20.750
moral narrative.

03:58:20.750 --> 03:58:25.550
A moral narrative that blames
poor people for our problems,

03:58:25.550 --> 03:58:29.160
that tries to pit us against
each other, and that claims

03:58:29.160 --> 03:58:32.180
that there is scarcity when
we're living in a society,

03:58:32.180 --> 03:58:33.480
in a world of abundance.

03:58:33.480 --> 03:58:36.890
And so, so we, we've said
that another one of the evils

03:58:36.890 --> 03:58:41.250
that we have to take on in this
day is this distorted moral

03:58:41.250 --> 03:58:42.550
narrative that is propagated

03:58:42.550 --> 03:58:45.380
by these religious
Christian nationalists.

03:58:45.380 --> 03:58:48.990
And, and that we have to,
we have to call that out,

03:58:48.990 --> 03:58:52.320
and we have to show that
something else is possible.

03:58:52.320 --> 03:58:54.790
And that a new narrative
is possible and,

03:58:54.790 --> 03:58:56.570
and coming through.

03:58:56.570 --> 03:59:00.090
So, so that's one of the
lessons that we, we took.

03:59:00.090 --> 03:59:03.160
Another, another lesson
is, is the need to organize

03:59:03.160 --> 03:59:07.380
and unite the poor across
all the lines that divide us.

03:59:07.380 --> 03:59:10.290
And so what you see in some of
the photos, and some of the,

