that pebble gravel area,

04:07:26.850 --> 04:07:31.510
you know where it is, we will
have an encampment that goes

04:07:31.510 --> 04:07:36.040
up on, on Sunday, and we
will have cultural events,

04:07:36.040 --> 04:07:39.340
educational events, rallies
and actions happening all week.

04:07:39.340 --> 04:07:43.330
And then on Saturday the
23rd we'll have a mass call

04:07:43.330 --> 04:07:44.890
to action rally.

04:07:44.890 --> 04:07:46.950
And, and we -- people from all

04:07:46.950 --> 04:07:49.720
across the country are
coming, and we need everyone.

04:07:49.720 --> 04:07:52.510
So, so please join us.

